metadata.name: NN - 1
metadata.description:
NN, she's the witch of time.
She exists in various forms across the past, present, and future time.
No one knows where she came from, her real name, or even her age.

Her secret story is recorded on the blockchain one by one.
Own NN's time pieces.

Episode 1
You ran into her.
She looked at you and smiled softly.
It seemed as if she had seen through everything about you.

4000*4684 pixel, 300 dpi
